le, rgba(46, 235, 157, 0.4) 0%, rgba(28, 150, 95, 0.2) 70%, transparent 100%);" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs></div> <div class="logo-glow-inner-digital-4 absolute inset-4 rounded-full blur-xl opacity-50" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(46, 235, 157, 0.5) 0%, rgba(28, 150, 95, 0.3) 60%, transparent 100%);" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs></div> <img id="digital-logo-4" src="/_astro/earth.WPTTsnmP.png" alt="Digital Twin Representation 4" class="opacity-0 relative w-64 h-64 max-w-[300px] max-h-[300px] object-contain z-0" width="300" height="300" style="filter: hue-rotate(120deg);" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs> </div> <div class="hud-interface absolute inset-[-30px] z-10 pointer-events-none" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs> <div id="hud-element-0" class="hud-element top-element opacity-0 absolute top-[10%] right-[1vw] z-10" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs> <div class="hud-content bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/30 rounded-md overflow-hidden" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs> <div class="hud-header bg-white/20 text-white text-xs font-mono p-1 pl-2 flex items-center" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs> <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-white mr-1.5 animate-pulse" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs></div>  Yield forecast </div> <div class="hud-body p-2 text-white" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs> <div class="font-mono text-sm font-bold" style="color: #2ebdeb" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs>10 t/ha</div> <div class="text-gray-300 text-xs" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs>Below seasonal average</div> </div> </div> </div><div id="hud-element-1" class="hud-element middle-element opacity-0 absolute top-[40%] right-[2vw] z-10" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs> <div class="hud-content bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/30 rounded-md overflow-hidden" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs> <div class="hud-header bg-white/20 text-white text-xs font-mono p-1 pl-2 flex items-center" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs> <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-white mr-1.5 animate-pulse" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs></div> Crop Stress </div> <div class="hud-body p-2 text-white" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs> <div class="font-mono text-sm font-bold" style="color: #9fb8a3" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs>Medium</div> <div class="text-gray-300 text-xs" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs>deficiency detected</div> </div> </div> </div><div id="hud-element-2" class="hud-element bottom-element opacity-0 absolute top-[70%] right-[1vw] z-10" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs> <div class="hud-content bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/30 rounded-md overflow-hidden" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs> <div class="hud-header bg-white/20 text-white text-xs font-mono p-1 pl-2 flex items-center" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs> <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-white mr-1.5 animate-pulse" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs></div> What if </div> <div class="hud-body p-2 text-white" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs> <div class="font-mono text-sm font-bold" style="color: #b37337" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs>Apply 10% less fertilizer</div> <div class="text-gray-300 text-xs" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs>Expected yield reduction: 2%</div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div id="trust-section" class="max-w-4xl mx-auto opacity-0 w-full" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs> <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-3 font-bold text-justify w-full" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs>The Digital Twin Component uses Earth Observation technology to create a precise digital replica of agricultural ecosystems. By utilizing satellite imagery and RS data, it provides <br> invaluable insights into arable land, including comprehensive analysis of soil and crop properties and conditions such as crop stress. Early identification of these stressors allows to take timely actions, enhancing crop resilience and optimal resource usage. <br> Advanced forecasting models are used to predict crop yields by analyzing historical yield data alongside recorded EO data, weather and soil conditions. This capability enables early insights in future harvests and allows for more effective resources usage and aids in economic forecasting. <br> A digital twin is not complete without the ability to change future conditions and see the effects of management actions on key parameters, such as yield. Scenario testing takes user input to test and assess different future climate and land management scenarios.</p> <div class="flex justify-center gap-x-6" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs> <div class="partner-logo py-1 px-3 bg-white/30 rounded text-gray-600 text-xs font-medium transform scale-90 transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out hover:scale-105" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs> Crop Monitoring </div><div class="partner-logo py-1 px-3 bg-white/30 rounded text-gray-600 text-xs font-medium transform scale-90 transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out hover:scale-105" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs> Yield Forecasting </div><div class="partner-logo py-1 px-3 bg-white/30 rounded text-gray-600 text-xs font-medium transform scale-90 transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out hover:scale-105" data-astro-cid-mmc7otgs> Scenario Testing </div> </div> </div> </div> </div>  <script type="module" src="/_astro/Welcome.astro_astro_type_script_index_0_lang.nIgxmG7X.js"></script></div> <section id="features" class="h-screen sticky z-20 top-0 overflow-hidden" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#a8c7bd] to-[#d8e8e0] z-0" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div class="shape-1 absolute rounded-full blur-[80px] w-1/2 h-1/2 -top-[10%] -right-[10%] bg-gradient-to-br from-[rgba(92,219,149,0.2)] to-[rgba(46,189,235,0.1)]" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp></div> <div class="shape-2 absolute rounded-full blur-[80px] w-2/5 h-2/5 -bottom-[10%] left-[10%] bg-gradient-to-br from-[rgba(179,115,55,0.15)] to-[rgba(92,219,149,0.1)]" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp></div> </div> <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5" aria-hidden="true" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div class="w-full h-full bg-grid-pattern" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp></div> </div> <div class="container relative z-10 mx-auto px-4 h-full flex flex-col justify-center" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div id="feature-header" class="text-center mb-[3vh] max-w-3xl mx-auto" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp data-astro-transition-scope="astro-fcpvgyrl-5"> <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/20 text-[#1c5f1e] text-sm font-medium my-3 md:mb-4" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> Digital Twins </div> <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-3 md:mb-4 leading-tight" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> Digital Twin Component for  <span class="text-[#1c5f1e]" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp>Agriculture</span> </h2> <p id="section-description" class="text-white text-base mx-auto" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> Build upon the DestinE and ESA Digital Twin Earth solution suit, this Digital Twin Component focusses to provide advanced tools and solutions for the agricultural sector. </p> </div> <!-- Desktop view: visible on md and up screens --> <div class="hidden md:block space-y-7 max-w-6xl mx-auto overflow-hidden pb-6 md:pb-0" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div class="feature-card flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-6 md:gap-8 lg:gap-16" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div class="order-1 md:order-2 w-full md:w-1/2 px-2 md:px-0" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div class="hidden md:flex feature-image rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg aspect-[4/3] flex-col items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0f172a] to-[#142a1b]" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <img src="/_astro/crops4eu_1.Dnfulf2f_1BfJ.webp" alt="Digital Twin" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp="true" width="495" height="495" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="w-full"> </div> </div> <div class="order-2 md:order-1 w-full md:w-1/2 px-2 md:px-0 mt-6 md:mt-0" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div class="feature-content bg-black/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-4 md:p-5 transition-all duration-300 hover:md:-translate-y-1" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div class="feature-header flex items-center space-x-3 mb-1 md:mb-2" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div class="bg-[#1c5f1e]/20 p-2 md:p-3 rounded-xl" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <span class="text-xl md:text-2xl" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp>🌱</span> </div> <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp>Digital Twin Technology</h3> </div> <p class="text-white mb-3 md:mb-4 text-xs" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp>Digital Twins are virtual replicas of physical systems using real-time data to simulate, analyze, and optimize their performance. This can be for example cropland systems. They enable getting insight in operations, maintenance, and improve decision making by providing representations of the ecosystems and processes and enabling trade-off analysis. This can be current states or future states (weeks or months in the future).</p> <ul class="space-y-2 mb-2 text-xs list-item pl-5" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <li class="feature-list-item flex items-start opacity-0 text-white" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-[#1c5f1e] mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp></path> </svg> <span data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> Monitoring: better understand the state of crops today </span> </li><li class="feature-list-item flex items-start opacity-0 text-white" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-[#1c5f1e] mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp></path> </svg> <span data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> Forecasting: understand what is expected in the future </span> </li><li class="feature-list-item flex items-start opacity-0 text-white" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-[#1c5f1e] mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp></path> </svg> <span data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> Decision making: test in the virtual world impacts to choose the best course of action </span> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div><div class="feature-card flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-6 md:gap-8 lg:gap-16" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div class="order-1  w-full md:w-1/2 px-2 md:px-0" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div class="hidden md:flex feature-image rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg aspect-[4/3] flex-col items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0f172a] to-[#142a3b]" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <img src="/_astro/crops4eu_2.DEjtiwMV_gh7M4.webp" alt="Agricultural Area" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp="true" width="1283" height="938" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="w-full h-full"> </div> </div> <div class="order-2  w-full md:w-1/2 px-2 md:px-0 mt-6 md:mt-0" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div class="feature-content bg-black/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-4 md:p-5 transition-all duration-300 hover:md:-translate-y-1" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div class="feature-header flex items-center space-x-3 mb-1 md:mb-2" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div class="bg-[#1c5f1e]/20 p-2 md:p-3 rounded-xl" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <span class="text-xl md:text-2xl" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp>📊</span> </div> <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1c5f1e]" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp>Example Agricultural application areas:</h3> </div> <p class="text-white mb-3 md:mb-4 text-xs" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp>Because of climate change and human interventions, heat extremes, drought, diseases, and pests will occur more often and will lead without adequate responses to crop productivity losses. Trade-offs have to be made to best support agricultural practices in a way that meets the current food and resource needs without compromising the ability of future generations to meet their own needs. The following areas can be supported with the aid of a digital twin:</p> <ul class="space-y-2 mb-2 text-xs list-item pl-5" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <li class="feature-list-item flex items-start opacity-0 text-white" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-[#1c5f1e] mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp></path> </svg> <span data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> Economic Viability: Ensuring that agricultural practices are economically sustainable, allowing them to maintain profitability while navigating the challenges posed by climate change. </span> </li><li class="feature-list-item flex items-start opacity-0 text-white" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-[#1c5f1e] mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp></path> </svg> <span data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> Resource Efficiency: maximizing the efficient use of resources, such as water and nutrients, to minimize waste and reduce environmental impact </span> </li><li class="feature-list-item flex items-start opacity-0 text-white" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-[#1c5f1e] mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp></path> </svg> <span data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> Environmental Stewardship: Utilizing practices that protect and enhance natural resources (soil health, water, etc.). </span> </li><li class="feature-list-item flex items-start opacity-0 text-white" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-[#1c5f1e] mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp></path> </svg> <span data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> Climate Resilience: Implementing practices that enhance the resilience of agricultural systems to climate change, recover from climate extremes and adapt to shifting climate conditions </span> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> <!-- Mobile view: swiper carousel, visible only on smaller screens --> <div class="md:hidden w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div class="swiper-container overflow-hidden" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div class="swiper-wrapper" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div class="swiper-slide px-2" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div class="feature-card flex flex-col h-full" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div class="w-full mt-0" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div class="feature-content bg-black/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-4 transition-all duration-300" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div class="feature-header flex items-center space-x-3 mb-2" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div class="bg-[#1c5f1e]/20 p-2 rounded-xl" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <span class="text-xl" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp>🌱</span> </div> <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#1c5f1e]" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp>Digital Twin Technology</h3> </div> <p class="text-white mb-3 text-xs" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp>Digital Twins are virtual replicas of physical systems using real-time data to simulate, analyze, and optimize their performance. This can be for example cropland systems. They enable getting insight in operations, maintenance, and improve decision making by providing representations of the ecosystems and processes and enabling trade-off analysis. This can be current states or future states (weeks or months in the future).</p> <ul class="space-y-2 mb-2 text-xs list-item pl-5" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <li class="feature-list-item flex items-start text-white" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-[#1c5f1e] mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp></path> </svg> <span data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> Monitoring: better understand the state of crops today </span> </li><li class="feature-list-item flex items-start text-white" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-[#1c5f1e] mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp></path> </svg> <span data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> Forecasting: understand what is expected in the future </span> </li><li class="feature-list-item flex items-start text-white" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-[#1c5f1e] mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp></path> </svg> <span data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> Decision making: test in the virtual world impacts to choose the best course of action </span> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div><div class="swiper-slide px-2" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div class="feature-card flex flex-col h-full" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div class="w-full mt-0" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div class="feature-content bg-black/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-4 transition-all duration-300" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div class="feature-header flex items-center space-x-3 mb-2" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <div class="bg-[#1c5f1e]/20 p-2 rounded-xl" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <span class="text-xl" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp>📊</span> </div> <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#1c5f1e]" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp>Example Agricultural application areas:</h3> </div> <p class="text-white mb-3 text-xs" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp>Because of climate change and human interventions, heat extremes, drought, diseases, and pests will occur more often and will lead without adequate responses to crop productivity losses. Trade-offs have to be made to best support agricultural practices in a way that meets the current food and resource needs without compromising the ability of future generations to meet their own needs. The following areas can be supported with the aid of a digital twin:</p> <ul class="space-y-2 mb-2 text-xs list-item pl-5" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <li class="feature-list-item flex items-start text-white" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-[#1c5f1e] mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp></path> </svg> <span data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> Economic Viability: Ensuring that agricultural practices are economically sustainable, allowing them to maintain profitability while navigating the challenges posed by climate change. </span> </li><li class="feature-list-item flex items-start text-white" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-[#1c5f1e] mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp></path> </svg> <span data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> Resource Efficiency: maximizing the efficient use of resources, such as water and nutrients, to minimize waste and reduce environmental impact </span> </li><li class="feature-list-item flex items-start text-white" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-[#1c5f1e] mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp></path> </svg> <span data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> Environmental Stewardship: Utilizing practices that protect and enhance natural resources (soil health, water, etc.). </span> </li><li class="feature-list-item flex items-start text-white" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-[#1c5f1e] mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp></path> </svg> <span data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp> Climate Resilience: Implementing practices that enhance the resilience of agricultural systems to climate change, recover from climate extremes and adapt to shifting climate conditions </span> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <!-- Add pagination dots --> <div class="swiper-pagination mt-4" data-astro-cid-rcfp6rtp></div> </div> </div> </div> </section>  <script type="module" src="/_astro/FeatureCards.astro_astro_type_script_index_0_lang.CHKaZB5B.js"></script> <section id="learn-more" class="h-screen sticky z-30 top-0 overflow-hidden" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#f9fbfc] to-[#e9f5fc] z-0" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <div class="shape absolute rounded-full blur-[80px]" style="background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(46, 189, 235, 0.3), rgba(28, 95, 30, 0.1)); width: 50%; height: 50%; top: -10%; right: -10%;" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c></div> <div class="shape absolute rounded-full blur-[80px]" style="background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(28, 95, 30, 0.2), rgba(46, 189, 235, 0.1)); width: 40%; height: 40%; bottom: -10%; left: 10%;" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c></div> </div> <div class="container relative z-10 mx-auto px-4 h-full flex flex-col justify-center" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <div id="header-content" class="text-center mb-8 md:mb-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c data-astro-transition-scope="astro-dqc2qutn-6"> <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-[#2ebdeb]/10 text-[#2ebdeb] text-sm font-medium mb-4" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> Satellite Monitoring Technology </div> <h2 class="text-4xl xl:text-5xl font-bold text-[#1c5f1e] mb-4 leading-tight" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> Scientific Foundational  <span class="text-[#2ebdeb]" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c>Pillars</span> </h2> <p id="section-description" class="text-sm xl:text-base text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> Satellite monitoring transforms raw data into advanced insight in the current state of croplands, advanced models allow to project future cropland states. As a standard this would be forecasting under normal conditions. Scenario testing further allows to test the evolution of a cropland system under specific prescribed scenarios. </p> </div> <!-- Desktop view: visible on lg and up screens --> <div id="main-content" class="hidden lg:flex max-w-6xl mx-auto w-full gap-8 lg:gap-16" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c data-astro-transition-scope="astro-safmmqqf-7"> <div id="features-container" class="w-2/5 space-y-6 order-1 xl:order-1" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <div class="feature-card bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-[#2ebdeb]/10 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1" data-index="0" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <div class="flex items-start" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <div class="bg-[#2ebdeb]/10 p-3 rounded-xl mr-4" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-[#2ebdeb]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" /> </svg> </div> <div data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <h3 class="text-md xl:text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c>Pillar 1: Crop Monitoring</h3> <p class="text-xs xl:text-sm text-gray-600" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c>Continuous monitoring allows to create a recent state of cropland ecosystems with advanced analysis, providing key insights in the health of plants, the stress they undergo and soil conditions.</p> </div> </div> </div><div class="feature-card bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-[#2ebdeb]/10 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1" data-index="1" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <div class="flex items-start" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <div class="bg-[#1c5f1e]/10 p-3 rounded-xl mr-4" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-[#1c5f1e]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" /> </svg> </div> <div data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <h3 class="text-md xl:text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c>Pillar 2: Yield Forecasting</h3> <p class="text-xs xl:text-sm text-gray-600" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c>Combining the monitored recent state of cropland ecosystems from the monitoring pillar with auxiliary data streams, such as seasonal weather forecast, will provide in season yield forecasting and a standard future state of the cropland system. This is a baseline forecast.</p> </div> </div> </div><div class="feature-card bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-[#2ebdeb]/10 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1" data-index="2" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <div class="flex items-start" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <div class="bg-[#b37337]/10 p-3 rounded-xl mr-4" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-[#b37337]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" /> </svg> </div> <div data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <h3 class="text-md xl:text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c>Pillar 3: Scenario Testing</h3> <p class="text-xs xl:text-sm text-gray-600" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c>What-if questions are at the heart of a digital twin. By combining the forecasting with advanced algorithms, the Digital Twin Component will be able to provide answers, for example, on trade-offs between water usage and crop yield optimization under drought effects. Or fertilization minimization while balancing yield and nitrogen soil content.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div id="image-container" class="w-3/5 order-2 xl:order-2 m-auto text-center" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <div class="max-h-[30vh] m-auto my-3 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg border border-white/20 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0f172a] to-[#1a2c4c] aspect-[4/3] flex flex-col items-center justify-center" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <img src="/_astro/crops4eu_3.DGhYppYo_15cwC3.webp" id="feature-image" alt="An image explaining the concept of crops4eu by the Luxembourg Institute of Science and Technology" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c="true" width="381" height="278" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="w-full h-full"> </div> <label for="feature-image" class="text-black" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c>Image Credits: Luxembourg Institute of Science and Technology</label> </div> </div> <!-- Mobile view: swiper carousel --> <div class="lg:hidden w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-8" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <div class="swiper-container overflow-hidden flex items-center" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <div class="swiper-wrapper" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <div class="swiper-slide px-3" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <div class="feature-card bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-[#2ebdeb]/10 h-full flex flex-col" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <div class="flex items-start mb-4" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <div class="bg-[#2ebdeb]/10 p-3 rounded-xl mr-4 flex-shrink-0" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-[#2ebdeb]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" /> </svg> </div> <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c>Pillar 1: Crop Monitoring</h3> </div> <div class="mt-3 flex-1" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c>Continuous monitoring allows to create a recent state of cropland ecosystems with advanced analysis, providing key insights in the health of plants, the stress they undergo and soil conditions.</p> </div> </div> </div><div class="swiper-slide px-3" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <div class="feature-card bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-[#2ebdeb]/10 h-full flex flex-col" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <div class="flex items-start mb-4" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <div class="bg-[#1c5f1e]/10 p-3 rounded-xl mr-4 flex-shrink-0" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-[#1c5f1e]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" /> </svg> </div> <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c>Pillar 2: Yield Forecasting</h3> </div> <div class="mt-3 flex-1" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c>Combining the monitored recent state of cropland ecosystems from the monitoring pillar with auxiliary data streams, such as seasonal weather forecast, will provide in season yield forecasting and a standard future state of the cropland system. This is a baseline forecast.</p> </div> </div> </div><div class="swiper-slide px-3" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <div class="feature-card bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-[#2ebdeb]/10 h-full flex flex-col" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <div class="flex items-start mb-4" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <div class="bg-[#b37337]/10 p-3 rounded-xl mr-4 flex-shrink-0" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-[#b37337]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" /> </svg> </div> <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c>Pillar 3: Scenario Testing</h3> </div> <div class="mt-3 flex-1" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c>What-if questions are at the heart of a digital twin. By combining the forecasting with advanced algorithms, the Digital Twin Component will be able to provide answers, for example, on trade-offs between water usage and crop yield optimization under drought effects. Or fertilization minimization while balancing yield and nitrogen soil content.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="swiper-pagination" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c></div> </div> </div> <div id="cta-button" class="mt-5 xl:mt-16 text-center" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-[#1c5f1e] text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-[#164518] transition-colors" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> Request More Information <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" data-astro-cid-lmkqoz2c></path> </svg> </a> </div> </div> </section>  <script type="module" src="/_astro/DataVisualization.astro_astro_type_script_index_0_lang.m-3A1bnB.js"></script> <section id="consortium" class="min-h-screen md:h-screen sticky z-30 top-0 overflow-hidden py-8 md:py-0" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so> <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#a8c7bd] to-[#d8e8e0] z-0" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so> <div class="shape-1 absolute rounded-full blur-[80px] w-1/2 h-1/2 -top-[10%] -right-[10%] bg-gradient-to-br from-[rgba(179,115,55,0.2)] to-[rgba(46,189,235,0.1)]" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so></div> <div class="shape-2 absolute rounded-full blur-[80px] w-2/5 h-2/5 -bottom-[10%] left-[10%] bg-gradient-to-br from-[rgba(92,219,149,0.15)] to-[rgba(179,115,55,0.1)]" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so></div> </div> <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5" aria-hidden="true" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so> <div class="w-full h-full bg-grid-pattern" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so></div> </div> <div class="container relative z-10 mx-auto px-4 h-full flex flex-col justify-center" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so> <div id="consortium-header" class="text-center mb-8 md:mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so data-astro-transition-scope="astro-2j5q3tk4-8"> <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-[#b37337]/10 text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium mb-3 md:mb-4" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so> European Collaboration </div> <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-3 md:mb-4 leading-tight" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so>  <span style="color: #b37337" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so>Consortium</span> </h2> <p class="text-base md:text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto text-white header-description" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so> The following entities are working on the Agricultural Digital Twin Component within SaveCrops4EU: </p> </div> <div id="consortium-partners" class="max-w-5xl mx-auto w-full" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so data-astro-transition-scope="astro-cwsx3qbp-9"> <!-- Desktop view: visible on md and up screens --> <div class="hidden md:grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-3 sm:gap-4 md:gap-6 partners-grid" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so> <div class="card-container min-h-[20rem]" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so> <div class="partner-card relative w-full h-full cursor-pointer overflow-hidden" data-index="0" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so> <!-- Card Front --> <div class="card-face card-front absolute inset-0 flex flex-col bg-white/30 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl border border-white/20 p-4 sm:p-5 md:p-6" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so> <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center h-full" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so> <div id="partner-image" class="h-[90px] p-3 sm:p-4 items-center justify-center mb-3 md:mb-4" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so> <img class="text-xs sm:text-sm" src="TAS.png" width="150px" height="90px" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so> </div> <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-bold mb-2 partner-name" style="color: #303980" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so>Thales Alenia Space Luxembourg</h3> <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-gray-700 mb-auto partner-description" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so>Thales Alenia Space in Luxembourg is a “Digital Competence Center” dedicated to ...</p> <button class="expand-btn mt-3 md:mt-4 inline-flex items-center text-xs font-medium text-gray-700 hover:text-gray-900 bg-white/40 hover:bg-white/60 rounded-full px-3 py-1 transition-colors" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so> <span class="btn-text" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so>More details</span> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-3.5 w-3.5 ml-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 8h16M4 16h16" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so></path> </svg> </button> </div> </div> <!-- Card Back --> <div class="card-face card-back absolute inset-0 flex flex-col bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-md rounded-xl border border-white/30 p-4 sm:p-5 md:p-6 shadow-lg opacity-0 pointer-events-none" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so> <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so> <div class="flex items-center" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so> <div class="mini-logo rounded-full bg-white/30 p-1.5 sm:p-2 w-8 sm:w-10 h-8 sm:h-10 flex items-center justify-center mr-2 sm:mr-3" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so> <img class="text-[0.65rem] sm:text-xs" src="TAS.png" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so> </div> <h3 class="text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg font-bold break-all" style="color: #303980" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so>Thales Alenia Space Luxembourg</h3> </div> <button class="collapse-btn p-1.5 rounded-full bg-white/30 hover:bg-white/50 text-gray-700 transition-colors" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so></path> </svg> </button> </div> <div class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto pr-2 text-gray-700 card-content" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so> <p class="mb-3 text-xs sm:text-sm leading-6 text-justify" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so>Thales Alenia Space in Luxembourg is a “Digital Competence Center” dedicated to space activities. It was incorporated in 2020 and is fully own by Thales Alenia Space, a joint venture between Thales (67%) and Leonardo (33%). Its operations began in January 2021, with a first project kick-off in September 2021. <br> Thales Alenia Space in Luxembourg leverages big data, artificial intelligence and cybersecurity to address complex end-to-end challenges, while fostering excellence in user experience. Its expertise covers innovative design and implementation approaches with customers, minimum viable products development, design and development of key digital building blocks of space systems, rollout and operations of solutions, experimentation of new technologies and concepts, digital business models, and international project management. Thales Alenia Space in Luxembourg also developed with Luxembourgish partners a Flooding Digital Twin Proof of Concept. <br> As part of SaveCrops4EU, Thales Alenia Space in Luxembourg manages the project coordination and system architecture design. It also ensures that the integration of the various scientific components into a pre-operational system is done consistently and according to industry standards. <br> Besides its own skills and heritage, Thales Alenia Space in Luxembourg can benefit from the support of and capitalize on both Thales Alenia Space’s and Thales’ legacy and expertise. Drawing on over 40 years of experience and a unique combination of skills, expertise and cultures, Thales Alenia Space delivers cost-effective solutions for telecommunications, navigation, Earth observation, environmental management, exploration, science and orbital infrastructures. Governments and private industry alike count on Thales Alenia Space to design satellite-based systems that provide anytime, anywhere connections and positioning, monitor our planet, enhance management of its resources, and explore our Solar System and beyond. Thales Alenia Space sees space as a new horizon, helping to build a better, more sustainable life on Earth. A joint venture between Thales (67%) and Leonardo (33%), Thales Alenia Space also teams up with Telespazio to form the parent companies’ Space Alliance, which offers a complete range of solutions including services. Thales Alenia Space has built several telecom, Earth observations and satellite navigation constellations. All the geostationary Meteosat weather satellites were built under the company’s prime contractorship, which is also the world leader in altimetry. Thales Alenia Space is a major partner onboard 11 out 12 Copernicus missions, a very sophisticated European program fully dedicated to environmental monitoring. The world leader in pressurized modules, the company built over 50% of the International Space Station’s habitable volume and will provide nearly 75% of Lunar Gateway’s pressurized volume. Gateway is the future space station that will orbit around the Moon. And yet, our company has contributed to numerous iconic space exploration missions across the solar system, including Cassini-Huygens for Saturn, BepiColombo for Mercury, ExoMars, Euclid, to name a few. The company is now developing a new telecommunications digitalized product line, Space INSPIRE, that is fully reprogrammable in orbit.Moreover, in direct relation to the Digital Twin Technologies, Thales Alenia Space was in charge in 2019 of ESA HLA Gaia-PHI high-level architecture study, participated in the Digital Twin Ocean precursor, and currently contributes to the DestinE Core System Platform Services program at system Level. <br> Contributors: Sander Rouwette, Brian Maguire, Jean-Baptiste Paolucci, Nicolas Jessel <br> Keywords: Digital Twin System Architecture, Digital System Solutions, Scientific component integration</p> <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-[0.65rem] sm:text-xs mt-3 sm:mt-4 partner-footer" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so> <a href="https://www.thalesaleniaspace.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline font-medium text-lg" style="color: #303980" data-astro-cid-j45jk4so>
